fields.customfield_12215: /HGW/Wi-Fi WPS/Common/PBC (Push Button Config) method/5GHz WPS PBC

fields.Action:
Activate WPS PBC process from the (WebUI / phy button).

Try to connect a 5GHz WLAN STA using the WPS PBC method.
fields.Expected Result:
STA is associated to the DUT.

	A ping to the DUT is succesfull and STA can connect to the WAN (f.ex. Internet browsing)

fields.description:
This test verifies if it is possible to connect a STA using WPS PBC method.

[Precondition]

	WiFi is on.

	Encryption: WPA2.

	WPS Enabled.
fields.summary: [WI-FI-WPS] WPS 5GHz - WPA2
